#                                              % Percentify %
[![PyPI Downloads](https://static.pepy.tech/personalized-badge/percentify?period=total&units=INTERNATIONAL_SYSTEM&left_color=BLACK&right_color=GREEN&left_text=downloads)](https://pepy.tech/projects/percentify)
